==English==

===Adjective===
'''recoverable'''

# Capable of being [[regain]]ed or [[recover]]ed.
# [[restorable|Restorable]] from sickness, faintness, danger, or the like.
# Capable of being brought back to a former [[condition]].
# [[obtainable|Obtainable]] from a [[debtor]] or [[possessor]]: as, the debt is recoverable.

